fields.description: Since 1932 Chatham Village has provided a remarkably gracious way of life for its residents, combining the charm of an English country village with the convenience of modern urban living.Today, Chatham Village continues to offer the same charm and character that provides exciting opportunities and benefits to residents.Sensitivity to a unique social character and rich architectural heritage, combined with a progressive spirit and new ideas, provide a vitality and life style that is truly incomparable.Chatham Village, after more than three quarters of a century, remains a timeless community that has kept up with the times.
